title: ‘Grey’s Anatomy’ Family Tree: How All 28 Docs Are Related (PHOTOS)
text:
NEXT Advertisement 
Remember when Callie Torres was hanging out with her Grey Sloan colleagues on Grey’s Anatomy and realized they’re all related through sex ? She wasn’t exaggerating. 
With the surgeons mixing business with pleasure so often, it’s hard to remember who birthed whom, who mentored whom, who sexed up whom, et cetera. But we think we have the Grey’s Anatomy relationships all sorted out. 
Click through the slideshow to see all 28 series regulars from the show’s past and and present — and how they relate to their coworkers and other significant folks.
